Ron and Lynda slowed down when they saw the signs for the city and exited into a dirt road. 
The city was mostly deserted. 
It looked like yet another nondescript city in the middle of nowhere.
But Ron was drawn to Mystique Valley for a reason.
As a Professor of Gerontology at the University of Southern California, Ron had noticed something unusual about the city from the research and census data.
Average age: 76
For Ron, this city was a godsend to do research work on aging populations. 
Over the last few weeks, he made multiple trips to the city to observe and interview the inhabitants. 

